source:
TEXT_BANARK119_04569_SEQ_00Maru seems concerned about dental hygiene.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANARK119_04569_SEQ_00 Schwierigkeitsanpassung (Job/Klasse darf nicht gewechselt werden)

Maru möchte die Eckzähne der Flusspferde pflegen.

source: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_TODO_00<tab>Place the rotting meat at the designated location.
TEXT_BANARK119_04569_TODO_01<tab>Lie in wait at the designated location and defeat the old pisaca when it appears.
TEXT_BANARK119_04569_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the handful of tough pisaca scales to Maru.
TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_000<tab>Our hippos are all sweet softies, but behind those plump, whiskery lips, they're packin' serious tusks that need regular care.
target: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_000<tab>Flusspferde sind ruhige und sanftmütige Wesen, aber ihre Eckzähne können eine Gefahr darstellen, wenn man sie wachsen lässt. Deshalb müssen wir sie regelmäßig stutzen.

source: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_001<tab>We like usin' pisaca scales to file 'em down, but pisaca scales have this tendency of comin' attached to pisaca. That's where you come in...
target: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_001<tab>Dafür brauchen wir etwas, das härter ist als die Zähne selbst. Kannst du eine Pisaca-Schuppe besorgen?

source: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_002<tab>If you leave this spoiled meat by their stampin' grounds, one's sure to come stampin'. Just make sure it ain't got brittle scales, okay? An old pisaca should have what you're lookin' for...
target: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_002<tab>Ich gebe dir einen Köder, mit dem du <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 02F22AD1020502 /var> anlocken kannst. Viel Erfolg!

source: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_011<tab>Oh, these are perfect! Thanks for your help.

TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_012<tab>So far as I know, pisaca scales are the only tool tough enough to handle Thavnairian hippo tusks. Wild hippos scrape theirs against giantsgall, but they can swallow bits of rock doin' that. Upsets their stomachs...
target: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_012<tab>Die Eckzähne eines Flusspferds wachsen, solange es lebt, und müssen gut gepflegt werden.

source: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_013<tab>But thanks to you, Svarna's hippos will have shaved tusks an' healthy bellies! The keystones of hippo health. ...Probably.
target: TEXT_BANARK119_04569_MARU_000_013<tab>Wild lebende Flusspferde feilen ihre Eckzähne an Felsen ab, aber dabei können Zahnsplitter abplatzen und verschluckt werden, was zu schweren Magenverletzungen führt. Sicherer ist es, wenn wir die Zähne sorgfältig abfeilen.
